ment</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTrackElement\"><code>HTMLTrackElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUListElement\"><code>HTMLUListElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLUnknownElement\"><code>HTMLUnknownElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLVideoElement\"><code>HTMLVideoElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HashChangeEvent\"><code>HashChangeEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/History\"><code>History</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Location\"><code>Location</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessageChannel\"><code>MessageChannel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Das&nbsp;<code>drag</code>&nbsp;Event wird ausgelöst, wenn ein Element oder ein Text \"gezogen\" wird&nbsp;(alle paar hundert Millisekunden).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"allgemeine_informationen","title":"Allgemeine Informationen","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"spezifikation\">Spezifikation</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\"><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.whatwg.org/specs/web-apps/current-work/multipage/dnd.html#event-drag\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5</a></dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"interface\">Interface</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">DragEvent</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"steigt_auf\">Steigt auf</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">Ja</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"abbrechbar\">Abbrechbar</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">Ja</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"ziel\">Ziel</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">Document, Element</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"standard-aktion\">Standard-Aktion</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">Mit der drag &amp; drop Operation fortfahren.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eigenschaften","title":"Eigenschaften","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Property</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Type</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Description</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>target</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\" title=\"EventTarget is an interface implemented by objects that can receive events and may have listeners for them.\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></td>\n   <td>The element that was underneath the element being dragged.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>type</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\" title=\"DOMString is a UTF-16 String. As JavaScript already uses such strings, DOMString is mapped directly to a String.\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n   <td>The type of event.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>bubbles</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\" title=\"The Boolean object is an object wrapper for a boolean value.\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Whether the event normally bubbles or not</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>cancelable</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\" title=\"The Boolean object is an object wrapper for a boolean value.\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Whether the event is cancellable or not?</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>view</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td><a class=\"new page-not-created\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WindowProxy\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\"><code>WindowProxy</code></a></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/defaultView\" title=\"In browsers, document.defaultView returns the window object associated with a document, or null if none is available.\"><code>document.defaultView</code></a> (<code>window</code> of the document)</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>detail</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td><code>long</code> (<code>float</code>)</td>\n   <td>0.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>dataTransfer</code></td>\n   <td>DataTransfer</td>\n   <td>The data that underlies a drag-and-drop operation, known as the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer\">drag data store</a>. Protected mode.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>currentTarget</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td>EventTarget</td>\n   <td>The node that had the event listener attached.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>relatedTarget</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td>EventTarget</td>\n   <td>For <code>mouseover</code>, <code>mouseout</code>, <code>mouseenter</code> and <code>mouseleave</code> events: the target of the complementary event (the <code>mouseleave</code> target in the case of a <code>mouseenter</code> event). <code>null</code> otherwise.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>screenX</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td>long</td>\n   <td>The X coordinate of the mouse pointer in global (screen) coordinates.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>screenY</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td>long</td>\n   <td>The Y coordinate of the mouse pointer in global (screen) coordinates.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>clientX</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td>long</td>\n   <td>The X coordinate of the mouse pointer in local (DOM content) coordinates.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>clientY</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td>long</td>\n   <td>The Y coordinate of the mouse pointer in local (DOM content) coordinates.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>button</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td>unsigned short</td>\n   <td>The button number that was pressed when the mouse event was fired: Left button=0, middle button=1 (if present), right button=2. For mice configured for left handed use in which the button actions are reversed the values are instead read from right to left.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>buttons</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td>unsigned short</td>\n   <td>The buttons being pressed when the mouse event was fired: Left button=1, Right button=2, Middle (wheel) button=4, 4th button (typically, \"Browser Back\" button)=8, 5th button (typically, \"Browser Forward\" button)=16. If two or more buttons are pressed, returns the logical sum of the values. E.g., if Left button and Right button are pressed, returns 3 (=1 | 2). <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent\">More info</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>mozPressure</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td>float</td>\n   <td>The amount of pressure applied to a touch or tabdevice when generating the event; this value ranges between 0.0 (minimum pressure) and 1.0 (maximum pressure).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>ctrlKey</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td>boolean</td>\n   <td><code>true</code> if the control key was down when the event was fired. <code>false</code> otherwise.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>shiftKey</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td>boolean</td>\n   <td><code>true</code> if the shift key was down when the event was fired. <code>false</code> otherwise.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>altKey</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td>boolean</td>\n   <td><code>true</code> if the alt key was down when the event was fired. <code>false</code> otherwise.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>metaKey</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td>boolean</td>\n   <td><code>true</code> if the meta key was down when the event was fired. <code>false</code> otherwise.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"dropzone\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div id<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"draggable\"</span> draggable<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"true\"</span> ondragstart<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"event.dataTransfer.setData('text/plain',null)\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span>\n        This div is draggable\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"dropzone\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"dropzone\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"dropzone\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>style<span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span>\n  #draggable <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">width</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> 200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">height</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    text<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>align<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> center<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">background</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> white<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dropzone <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">width</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> 200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">height</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">background</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> blueviolet<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    margin<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>bottom<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">padding</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>style<span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> dragged<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/* Event wird vom ge-drag-ten Element ausgelöst */</span>\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"drag\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"dragstart\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// Speichern einer ref auf das drag-bare Element</span>\n      dragged <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// Element halb-transparent machen</span>\n      event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>opacity <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"dragend\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// Transparenz zurücksetzen</span>\n      event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>opacity <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/* events fired on the drop targets */</span>\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"dragover\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// Standard-Aktion verhindern um das drop-Event zu erlauben</span>\n      event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">preventDefault</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"dragenter\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// Hintergrund des möglichen Drop-Zeils anfärben, wenn das drag-bare Element auf das Ziel gezogen wird</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>className <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"dropzone\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>background <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"purple\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"dragleave\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// Hintergrund des möglichen Drop-Ziels, wenn das drag-bare Element vom Ziel wieder weggezogen wird / verlässt</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>className <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"dropzone\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>background <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"drop\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">event</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// Standard-Aktion verhindern (Bei einigen Elementen wäre das das Öffnen als Link)</span>\n      event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">preventDefault</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// move dragged elem to the selected drop target</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>className <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"dropzone\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>background <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n          dragged<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>parentNode<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> dragged <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n          event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">appendChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> dragged <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"verwandte_events","title":"Verwandte Events","isH3":false,"content":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/drag_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">drag (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/dragstart_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">dragstart (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/dragend_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">dragend (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/dragover_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">dragover (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/dragenter_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">dragenter (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/dragleave_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">dragleave (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/Reference/Events/dragexit\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">dragexit</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/drop_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">drop (en-US)</a></code></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Allgemeine Informationen","id":"allgemeine_informationen"},{"text":"Eigenschaften","id":"eigenschaften"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"beispiel"},{"text":"Verwandte Events","id":"verwandte_events"}],"summary":"Das drag Event wird ausgelöst, wenn ein Element oder ein Text \"gezogen\" wird (alle paar hundert Millisekunden).","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"DragEvent","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"DragEvent","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"DragEvent","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"DragEvent","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"DragEvent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"DragEvent","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/dragevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/dragevent/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/DragEvent","title":"DragEvent"}],"pageTitle":"DragEvent - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}